{
  "stem": "5644.6",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "To make something clear, how we thinking of being free, is two days before we send out a Jewish couple, a men-- two men-- two people to up about four, five stories.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we said to them to watch our around-- what is around us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because we heard-- yeah, we heard Russian songs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the Russian is the Russians which work with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we asked-- we asked the boys to go in to-- we drew--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I lost.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I went out to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I went out together to watch them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I came back with a story.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As this is 3 kilometers the front between the Germans and the Russians, if you got anti-aircraft guns, you're putting a flag of your nation next to the-- to the anti-aircraft.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because the planes are running such a short distance, that I can kill your own people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But how do you know that the enemy won't see it?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They won't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because the Russians or the Germans know quite well the sound of the plane which is their's and which is the Russian's, They can--",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I knew, too.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So if I see that the Germans are running, I taking away their flag and starting to shoot at the planes.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because this is called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If it's very short, you've got to put the flag.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when the boys came back, they said to me, we are in trouble.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A red flag around [INAUDIBLE] with [NON-ENGLISH] in the center.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We got the Germans in our yard.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Watch out in the night time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Don't talk too much.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Don't cook.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We're going to be shut up for the few days--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--till the guns goes away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What was it there?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That wasn't a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
